{"tid":1730200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警謊宣佈今晚10點前不撤連記者都拘捕係不合法","createTime":"2019-11-17T12:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T13:56:43.000Z","uid":170160,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"140288cfbbb92c38021bb0685378fac0a96cabb6","tid":1730200,"uid":170160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"除左政府正式宣佈戒嚴或宵禁，否則警謊單方面宣佈，22:00 後記者唔撤離理大現場，如果繼續公平公正地現場報導，都會一律作出拘捕 !<br />\n<br />\n其實香港特區政府，唔正式向阱宣佈戒嚴或宵禁，根本冇法律理據咁做，佢地咁做估計係今晚會重演8.31，入內會瘋狂暴打違法拘捕，一個都唔會放過，所以就想走嚇記者會拘捕 !? 雖然現在 POPO 隨時都可拘捕任何人，但對於記者係告唔入暴動罪 !<br />\n<br />\n泛民法律議員有冇人挺身俾法律意見? 唔好匿埋一邊好喎!? 否則任由 POPO 衝入城大清場拘捕，隨時又有好多不明、但又一律冇可疑自殺案發生，大家小心! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dbc018d01260387231d0e46e7df1d5abb288019","tid":1730200,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"bf60b4effe3d6156d8cd2003c0d955efcc4b19c9","tid":1730200,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:53:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e720c6c6d224004b84ab1de3e34718d9b8057890","tid":1730200,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"想殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd550182d47ff2bc410c25d17a7ff2d9e800a1b","tid":1730200,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:53:42.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"3c32c9ea2dfadb19c3de13a57b05357c47b3091e","tid":1730200,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"記者唔好走，採訪職責嚟，點告得入"},{"pid":"a09c58586892146aab5ce0307a9fe2c58c10f9ea","tid":1730200,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:00:1